<span class="rating">Rating<span style="background-color: #ffffff;">0/0=0.00</span></span>
  </p>
  <div class="comment_content">
	<div class="comment_body">
	  <p>Squeak Smalltalk で。Balloon3D というパッケージを用いて正十二面体を回転させました。</p>

	</div>
	
	<p class="link">
	  see: <a href="/web/20081121105417/http://wiki.squeak.org/squeak/2713">Balloon3D - a tutorial</a>
	</p>  
	
	
	
    <div class="compact">
      <table><tr><td class="linenos"><pre>1
2
3
4
5
6
7
8
9</pre></td><td class="code"><div class="highlight"><pre>| sceneObj view solid colors |
solid := B3DRegularSolid dodekahedron.
colors := (Color wheel: 12) collect: [:each | each asB3DColor].
solid setFaceColors: colors.
sceneObj := B3DSceneObject named: &#39;solid&#39;.
sceneObj geometry: solid.
view := AdvancedB3DSceneMorph new.
view scene objects: (OrderedCollection with: sceneObj).
view beRotating; openInHand
</pre></div>
</td></tr></table>
    </div>
	

  
